                    <span>My husband and I are experienced boaters. We wanted to purchase a small cruiser and needed a little more education on the pros and cons of new vs. used. JP's book was well thought out and a great help. We found a beautiful used boat that suited our needs perfectly. The inspection checklist was instrumental in guiding us toward a quality boat at a substancial savings. Thanks JP!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">No meat to this book</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
