                    <span>Mr. Lamy's book has alleviated many of the fears I had regarding the purchase of a new/used boat. His thoughts on how to deal with sales people is priceless. This book should be read by any person interested in buying or selling a small power boat. <BR>I would love to see him write a book on general maintenance.</span>
                  
